subtitle: sacred beings of Earth I am zuk of
Andromeda and we are the andromedan
Council of light and we are here to
serve and assist you Humanity's division
stems from the illusion of Separation a
misconception that blinds people to the
fundamental interconnectedness of all
life many believe they hold a special
connection to the Divine While others do
not often due to deeply ingrained
religious or political
ideologies this mindset rooted in
judgment whether of others actions
appearances or beliefs creates a Chasm
that stifles spiritual growth and
prevents Unity
if you find yourself at odds with the
broader World it may be a reflection of
this Discord the violence and conflict
rampant in the world are not aligned
with the vibration of Oneness they are
manifestations of the illusion of
Duality however it is crucial not to
engage in a battle against those who
perpetuate these illusions
nor should you attempt to mold your
reality to fit
theirs many struggle to reconcile the
apparent chaos of the world with the
idea of an Ascension into love and light
how can a world so filled with violence
and death be on a path to higher
Consciousness similarly there is a
disconnect between those who seek peace
without religious affiliation
and those who cling to traditional
religious beliefs viewing others as
Outsiders or even
adversaries this divide seems
insurmountable to
many every experience you encounter no
matter how small offers a choice a
chance to align with your true
preferences when You Face illness you
naturally desire Health when you you
stumble you wish for stability when your
vision blurs you seek Clarity these
moments of contrast are opportunities to
choose to refine your path toward ease
Clarity and
well-being for those who are already
awakened it is time to examine any
lingering
prejudices even toward those who might
seem deserving of judgment
the true challenge is to release these
judgments and become the example of
unity and compassion that Humanity so
desperately
needs your role is not to divide further
but to help expand human consciousness
through your own actions and
attitudes remember you don't need to
earn your place in this higher
consciousness you don't need to belong
to a specific group or adhere to certain
beliefs your path is simply to relax
receive and embrace what is already
within you many beings including us are
here to support you in this journey as
more of humanity Embraces this
understanding the path forward will
become smoother and shorter
